Problem--> 

geeksforgeeks.org/problems/count-odd-even/1?page=1&category=Arrays&difficulty=Basic&status=solved,unsolved&sortBy=submission

Given an array arr[] of positive integers. The task is to return the count
of the number of odd and even elements in the array.

Ans-->

class Solution {
    public int[] countOddEven(int[] arr) {
        int E=0;
        int O=0;
        for(int ele :arr)
        {
            if(ele%2==0)
            {
                 E++;
            }
            else
            {
                 O++;
            }
        }
        return new int [] {O,E};
        
        
    }
}
